					<li id="fn3"><em>Milkmaid by Vermeer and Dutch Genre Painting Masterworks from the Rijksmuseum Amsterdam</em> was held from September 29 to December 17, 2007.<a href="#ref3">↩</a></li>
            	</ol>
            </div>
